title: Rembrandt and His Pupils (Art Ebook).pdf

Rembrandt and His Pupils
Robert Stockwell Limited | 1969 | English/French | 252 pages | PDF | 30.5 MB

A loan exhibition of paintings commemorating the 300th anniversary of Rembrandt, under the high patronage of His Excellency Dr. Theodorus Bot, Ambassador of the Netherlands to Canada. The Montreal Museum of Fine Arts, Montreal, January 9-February 23, 1969; Art Gallery of Ontario, Toronto, March 14-April 27, 1969
